get.description:
GET /files - File 목록 조회.

### Python (httpx)
```python
import httpx

BASE_URL = 'https://{domain}/agent/a{idx}'
url = BASE_URL + '/anthropic/files'
params = {
    'after_id': None,
    'before_id': None,
    'limit': 10,
}
# None 값은 제거하는 편이 안전합니다.
params = {k: v for k, v in params.items() if v is not None}

res = httpx.get(url, params=params, timeout=60)
res.raise_for_status()
print(res.json())
```

### Node.js (node-fetch)
```js
import fetch from 'node-fetch';

async function main() {
  const BASE_URL = 'https://{domain}/agent/a{idx}';
  const url = new URL(BASE_URL + '/anthropic/files');

  const params = new URLSearchParams({
    limit: '10',
    // after_id: '...',
    // before_id: '...',
  });
  url.search = params.toString();

  const res = await fetch(url, { method: 'GET' });
  if (!res.ok) throw new Error(res.status + ' ' + (await res.text()));
  console.log(await res.json());
}

main();
```

post.description:
POST /files - 파일 업로드.

### Python (httpx)
```python
import httpx

BASE_URL = 'https://{domain}/agent/a{idx}'
url = BASE_URL + '/anthropic/files'

with open('path/to/file.bin', 'rb') as f:
    res = httpx.post(url, files={'file': f}, timeout=60)

res.raise_for_status()
print(res.json())
```

### Node.js (node-fetch)
```js
import fetch from 'node-fetch';
import FormData from 'form-data';
import fs from 'node:fs';

async function main() {
  const BASE_URL = 'https://{domain}/agent/a{idx}';
  const url = BASE_URL + '/anthropic/files';

  const form = new FormData();
  form.append('file', fs.createReadStream('path/to/file.bin'));

  const res = await fetch(url, {
    method: 'POST',
    body: form,
    headers: form.getHeaders(),
  });

  if (!res.ok) throw new Error(res.status + ' ' + (await res.text()));
  console.log(await res.json());
}

main();
```

