get.description:
GET /files/{file_id}/content - File 바이너리 다운로드.

### Python (httpx)
```python
import httpx

BASE_URL = 'https://{domain}/agent/a{idx}'
file_id = 'YOUR_FILE_ID'
url = BASE_URL + f'/anthropic/files/{file_id}/content'

res = httpx.get(url, timeout=60)
res.raise_for_status()

with open('download.bin', 'wb') as f:
    f.write(res.content)

print('saved: download.bin')
```

### Node.js (node-fetch)
```js
import fetch from 'node-fetch';
import fs from 'node:fs';

async function main() {
  const BASE_URL = 'https://{domain}/agent/a{idx}';
  const fileId = 'YOUR_FILE_ID';
  const url = BASE_URL + '/anthropic/files/' + encodeURIComponent(fileId) + '/content';

  const res = await fetch(url, { method: 'GET' });
  if (!res.ok) throw new Error(res.status + ' ' + (await res.text()));

  const buf = Buffer.from(await res.arrayBuffer());
  fs.writeFileSync('download.bin', buf);
  console.log('saved: download.bin');
}

main();
```

